<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 07:06:08 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1e80dd94b27</link><description>&lt;p&gt;定制版“大”早餐，不要香肠。炒菠菜和蘑菇确实美味。可爱的沙拉也起到了作用。鸡蛋？超级棒！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Customized “big” breakfast, no sausage. Sauted spinach and mushroom are legit delish. Cute salad played its part too. The egg? Superb!" height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/seth/6a1e80dd94b27.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://seth.some.pics"&gt;@seth&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 07:06:08 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>数码相机</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1e51ff2615e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;数码相机&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Digicam" height="8176" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ogbee/6a1e51ff2615e.jpg" width="5136"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ogbee.some.pics"&gt;@ogbee&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 03:46:11 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1e4e84e6391</link><description>&lt;p&gt;简短社会杂志&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="The Society of Brevity Zine" height="2550" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/milo/6a1e4e84e6391.png" width="3300"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://milo.some.pics"&gt;@milo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 03:31:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>夏夜萤火虫之美</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1e3dce2661a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我今晚意识到，我真的、真的喜欢这个时节。已经晚上九点多了，日落刚刚结束，萤火虫出来了，外面真是太美了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Early night photo of Lawrence Arts Center building. A large tree features in the center. The sky is a deep blue." height="2783" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/swrogers/6a1e3dce2661a.jpg" width="3710"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://swrogers.some.pics"&gt;@swrogers&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 02:20:01 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>桥上观日落</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1e38ba49d81</link><description>&lt;p&gt;当我过桥回去看日落时，真是个美好的夜晚。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A cloudy sunset over a harbor, with the sun's glare on the water, a distant city skyline, and a dark, rocky shoreline in the foreground." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/6a1e38ba49d81.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 01:58:25 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>